videos.description: Nick Weiler-Babb pokes the ball free on the defensive end and runs the floor to get a tough layup to fall despite getting fouled.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Weiler-Babb turns defense into offense

videos.description: Nick Weiler-Babb continues his defensive dominance with a big block for the Cyclones in the first half.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Weiler-Babb denies Texas Tech

videos.description: Donovan Jackson hits his defender with a dirty crossover to create space and then sinks the 3-pointer for the Cyclones.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Jackson gets saucy, drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Cameron Lard squares up his defender and gets the jumper to fall in the first half.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Lard sinks mid-range jumper

videos.description: Jarrett Culver is the lucky recipient of a broken alley-oop in the first half for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech gets rare double alley-oop to fall

videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith defies gravity for 360 dunk

videos.headline: Texas Tech head coach falls down while coaching

videos.headline: Lard has big role in Iowa State win
